Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:11.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}青ざめた町並
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:15.80,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}搖れる僕の影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:24.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}鈍い足取りは　行く先を知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.04,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}交わせぬ　想い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:38.37,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}君の瞳の中　映し出すものを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}受け止める為に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:46.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:52.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}差し出す　その手を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:01:00.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}ほどけないように　握り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:08.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}半分の月の夜は　僕らを照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:15.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}追いかけて來た時間を　僕は振り切って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:26.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}半分ずつの僕らは　描く先までも　見える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:11.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}染成一片蔚藍的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:15.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}我徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:24.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}拖著沉重的腳步不知該往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:30.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}無法交織的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:38.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}為了接受在你眼中倒映出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:46.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}我飛奔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:52.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}絕不放開你伸出的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:01:00.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}我緊緊將其握住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.07,0:01:08.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}夜晚半月的光輝映照著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:15.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}我擺脫那追逐不休的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:26.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(80,80)}半成熟的我們知道該如何描繪人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:47.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　指先であなたを感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:23:00.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　あなたと見ていたこの景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:13.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伝わる　優しさに身をゆだねて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:24.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永遠など無い　わかっていたつもりだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:33.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}名前を呼ぶ　あなたの聲を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:39.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸の奧に　しまっておくから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:45.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}開かれた　扉の向こう側で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:52.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれぬように　消えないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:47.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我還記得  指尖傳來的你的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.86,0:23:00.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}還記得嗎  這與你一同眺望的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.83,0:23:13.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我寄身於你對我的這份溫柔之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:24.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我相信我已經看透了世上沒有永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:33.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你呼喚我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:39.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我一直深埋心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:45.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了能在敞開的門那一側
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:52.60,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永不流失  永不消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:53.56,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,355)}{\fad(800,10)}多田珍藏品的繼承
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  救救裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身體狀況那麼差還劇烈運動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  今年你就在醫院過年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來馬上就能出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間靜靜休養吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你也應該累得不想活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了嗎傻瓜  再這樣就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了心上人的話就奮力去追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要退縮  退縮的話只能留下悔恨而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒做就放棄的話是最沒用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那多田先生你最後對她說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎  我是個傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為我是傻瓜才懷著悔恨而生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔真是件痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在聖誕夜決定幹什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  為什麼變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是病人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香你才是重病人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  你還不能起床的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾起一下也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為父親的事而帶你去炮台山的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是特地帶我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  在炮台山倒下的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  所以  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對里香你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體還不能活動  怎麼還搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭腦裡肯定是空白一片  肯定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像空噹噹的瓶子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲兩下的話一定會有彭彭的響聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是充滿青春活力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是什麼  是麵包還是要喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著這麼照顧我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不知道我能活到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的清楚點  你在我身邊對你沒什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定會動手術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎 難度很高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動手術的話壽命只會越來越短而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手術的話也許還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經做好思想準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  不要因為太得意而又溜出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我又要用長凳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局部地區傍晚會有小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎  戎崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是山西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷淡啊  我特地來看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你的目的就是為了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  原來你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  果然很驚人呢  戎崎珍藏品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共有幾本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多田珍藏品  不是我收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這遺產是你繼承的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒  戎崎你也要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎借幾本  給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量好驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  真是個厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  你還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香  能讓我進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我說了你就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血  血流了這麼多出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打伏擊戰還真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香對不起  是我不好  我道歉  你原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都為你做  每一天都去去圖書館\N借你喜歡的書  求你原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然上鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是感冒  先讓醫生來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肝炎惡化的話就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在那種地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被關在外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她看見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得肚子痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著笑得那麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊可是差點沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  乾脆死掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對你來說大概是個重傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目醫生你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我結束了休假就馬上回來了  真是個會使喚人的醫院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喉嚨疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼冷的天  還悠閒地去看星星了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  在曬太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:12:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒感到冷之前還是回去吧  感冒還沒好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識我了嗎  我是夏目  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目醫生  你的鬍子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了山裡  整整兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦啊  剛下山就被叫回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休假因此也掛掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在理髮店都剃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像被里香討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我發了很多牢騷  真的很生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是很容易發脾氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超愛發脾氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識里香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識是當然的  因為我是她的主治醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主治醫生  那麼心臟方面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情你從哪裡得知的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真少見啊  她會主動向別人說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我與里香相處的這6年之中\N她從未向別人透露過自己的病情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那種性格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在還沒有過朋友  也沒打算交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以或許有一個可以傾訴病情的人對於里香來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戎崎  現在開始你還是和里香好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是很重要的  是個能相伴說話的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和戀人不同  朋友的話會有許多隔閡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有的人說男孩和女孩不會有友情  但那是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你和里香不就是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香就拜託你了  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害嘛  在學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸煙有害健康
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對病人做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在和里香吵架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香還真是頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的小鬼藏個一兩本A書是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不止一兩本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像也有點迷茫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她不會流露出自己的心情  我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點失落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會流露出自己的心情是說里香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會生氣也會笑的  里香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一  里香會到這來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫她來的  這次你要做的利落點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下跪道歉什麼的是一定要的  里香也想和好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕羞恥去創造契機  這也是男人應有的氣度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個恩情一生也別忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  里香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  給你個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從外國直接進口的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  我並不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自長輩的好意就該收下  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香你誤會了  這是有理由的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了要戒煙的  為什麼還帶著打火機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸煙有害健康
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  谷崎  難道說我被討厭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  你說話太直言不諱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  在像這樣談話的時候老是笑咪咪的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說你這樣玩弄裕一我實在看不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一和里香都很吃不消啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要做這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是主治醫生你該知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒多少時間能在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連那一點時間也被你毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做那麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很令人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  谷崎  你去說服里香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這又是吹的哪股風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香  好想見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個  天氣不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風也很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又笨又囉嗦又好色  最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你再有討厭的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭裕一了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  發現航跡雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  要飛向何處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛到國外就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪  又不是向著裕一你飛過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎  飛向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在想色色的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  里香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會原諒我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏目醫生和我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.40,0:21:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏目醫生說你原諒他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.90,0:21:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去之前那所醫院時  一直很關注我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏目醫生調到這所醫院來了  所以我也轉院了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是按夏目醫生說的去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他那麼說了  所以你才來和我說話的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則絕對絕對不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣的傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的書
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在醫院裡 里香一直都是靠讀書來消磨時光的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書是里香父親留下的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  仰望半月的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:16.59,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(565,375)}{\fad(10,10)}戎崎珍藏品的終結～然後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既漫長又艱苦的住院生活
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里香一直都是靠讀書來消磨這段時光的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.45,0:24:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本書是里香父親留下的珍貴的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.36,0:24:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  手術  里香  炮台山  銀河鐵道之夜  還有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.09,0:24:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  仰望半月的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:46.72,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(565,375)}{\fad(10,10)}戎崎珍藏品的終結～然後
